Frequently asked questions

How to register a company in South African IDZ.

An IDZ company will be incorporated in the same way as a simple LLC. However, the IDZ company will be required to obtain a special license from the Department of Trade and Industry.

Does South Africa have a one stop facility for incorporating IDZ companies?

Currently, the Department of Trade and Industry is working on creating a one stop shop facility which will assist Clients with project planning, licensing requirements, financial assistance and assistance with provision of basic utilities.
